The paper discusses the application of natural language processing techniques, specifically word embeddings, on source code. This topic falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category, as it aims to improve the understanding and analysis of source code. However, the paper also involves the use of machine learning and data-driven approaches, which are relevant to the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), programming languages (cs.PL), and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
